Necromancer/Hell Drak

	Necromancer took a step back, as he could sense a touch of anger in
Dinobot's words.

	"My name is Necromancer, and this is my-" Necromancer was interrupted by
Hell Drak.

	"Look, my name's Hell Drak.  Got it?" She said and then turned to
Necromancer, "He didn't want to know about how we're related, okay? Just
keep it simple, bro!"
